Janmashtami marks the birth of Lord Krishna, who is believed to be the eighth incarnation of Lord Vishnu on Earth. The legend behind Lord Krishna's birth and his triumph over enemies makes for one of the Hindu folklore's most recited tales. 
Kashiyatra sends to you the warmest wishes on this pious festival. Let's embrace the teachings of Lord Krishna, the symbol of righteousness!

#HappyKrishnaJanmashtami
#Lord #Krishna #Janmashtami #MatkiPhod #DahiHandi 
#KY18 #Wishes #Kashiyatra #Cultural #Festival

It's impossible to wake up from a dream if the dawn is itself dark! Kashiyatra for us is a dream, an imagination filled with the top notch extravaganza! 
Team KY is thrilled to disclose the theme of the Upcoming edition of Kashiyatra. We are now geared to find exhilaration and jubilation in the darkness!
#Kashiyatra #KY18 #ThemeIsOut
#AStygianDawn  #LongNight

Our very own Cultural Council, IIT BHU Varanasi is organizing Aagman, Inter-branch cultural competitions exclusively for freshers' at IIT BHU this weekend.
Team Kashiyatra wishes all the freshers good luck!

Navratri begins with the reverence of Goddess Shailputri. She is believed to be the embodiment of divinity of Brahma, Vishnu and Mahesh. The colour of first day is red depicting action and vigour.
Kashiyatra wishes you with all the warmth and fervour a Happy Navratri Sthapana!

#HappyNavratri #Day1 #Red #Shailputri 
#Kashiyatra #KY18 #AStygianDawn

Let all the excitement fill into the air as we unveil the much-awaited theme for upcoming edition of Kashiyatra, the annual Socio-cultural festival of IIT(BHU) Varanasi.
We launch the theme for Kashiyatra’18 in a pre-event. The various clubs of the Cultural Council are all set to paint your evening into a delightful delineation as they boast their talents.
Venue - Limbdi Corner, IIT (BHU) Varanasi 
We hope to see you there!

Teacher is the one selfless person who acts as a guide throughout one's life. They presents the past, reveals the present, and creates the future.
Team KY pays whole hearted gratitude to all the teachers out there by wishing them a very #HappyTeachersDay!
#Culture #Teacher #Guru #Guide #Mentor
#Kashiyatra #CultFest #IIT #Varanasi
#KY18 #KYcomeswithwinter

#CampusAmbassadorProgram
Register at : http://www.kashiyatra.org
Everyone might like to start-off an amazing journey, but it's only a few who can actually take the lead and guide the rest, all along the way towards their destination.
Kashiyatra's #CampusAmbassador is one such position which is definitely meant for all such leaders who can lead the crowd and represent them. Be the face of KY in your college or city, take our awesomeness to your people and win exciting prizes from us.
#KY18 #CAP #Leader #Prize
#Kashiyatra #CultFest #IIT #Varanasi

In the list of Best Campus Ambassadors of KY'17, we introduce Aprajita Singh from Sunbeam College, Varanasi. 
She shared her experience of Kashiyatra with us as :
“It was one of the best experiences wherein I got the opportunity of what I am passionate about. It was a platform to enhance my hand on leadership, convincing skills and lots more to work in a team.
Pleasing personality and making the gathering understand the importance of the chances, opportunity or choices made me get 103 participants.
Everything like events, competitions, pronites and whole atmosphere of campus during the fest was amazing and i am eagerly waiting for KY'18 to feel that atmosphere again.”

We are bringing next candidate from the best Campus Ambassadors of KY'17.
Karthik Guduru - Amity, Lucknow
Here is his experience of KY’17 which he shared with us :
“Its been a great privilege and honour for me to be the part of CA program for Kashiyatra. It brought me the possibilities to realize my true potential and patience. This experience made me feel special and will always persist as unforgettable memory in my career.
I got all events access especially those wonderful pronites and various other different goodies. 
My focus was mainly aimed at comparing my skills with my friends which was very well attained with the help of team KY. That was an amazing experience of 2 months working as a CA,
and now i am looking forward to be the part of KY’18. I am highly obliged to team KY for connecting me to this wonderful extravaganza and giving me special focus and respect."

#Kashiyatra #CultFest
#KY17 #CAdiaries
#KY18 #KYcomeswithwinter

Next in the list of Best Campus Ambassadors of KY'17, we are introducing Maulshree Srivastava from BBD, Lucknow. 
She shared her experience with KY as :
“The authority of being something got me interested in becoming Campus Ambassador for KY'17 and i worked really hard for it. My contacts and convincing nature being added up by the cooperativeness of team KY, made my term successful.
The whole team of KY'17 was amazing. The job of handling such a huge fest and participation and still being that calm and sweet was commendable.
Getting known about what it takes to stand out from the crowd, cool goodies, crazy vouchers and all the fun in Varanasi have still left me into the KY mode."

#Kashiyatra #CultFest
#KY17 #CAdiaries
#KY18 #KYcomeswithwinter

We are introducing the Best Campus Ambassadors of KY'17.
Arun Kumar - IIITDM, Jabalpur
He narrated his experience as:
“An established online presence, high level of professionalism, natural leadership skill and passion for building and growing connections made me a successful Campus Ambassador. 
I was hugely impressed by the team KY. Managing every minute details with meticulous precision was the hallmark of the organising team which made the fest successful. We, the team of 85 members spent a gala time at the Kashiyatra and shared some good memories at the beautiful campus of Banaras Hindu University and Varanasi. 
Going for the Kashiyatra at least once in your lifetime is a worthwhile experience....and i am lucky to enjoy this experience last year and looking forward to visit again."

#Kashiyatra #CultFest
#KY17 #CAdiaries
#KY18 #KYcomeswithwinter
As the wait for winter has started, so is the wait for Kashiyatra. The cultural extravaganza is just 100 Nights away from now. Till then let the pre-events cater your craving for KY'18.

The crowded campus, familiar faces, pending parties, countless conversations, sleepless nights.. The big day has finally arrived which made the good byes back then less painful, promising to visit the dear ones on this occasion. Kashiyatra welcomes the class of 2017 to their Convocation Ceremony and congratulates each one of them on their successful journey so far. May your dreams and aspirations get fulfilled and scale the heights of success.
#Kashiyatra #KY18
#KYisComing #AStygianDawn #Convocation

Kashiyatra proudly presents the after-movie of KY'17 to give you the glimpses of A Millennial Reprise. Take a moment's pause and devour some of the most cherished and enraptured memories of KY'17 & stay tuned to experience A Stygian Dawn and get lost in the world of darkness in this year's edition of Kashiyatra.

Visit us at our website: www.kashiyatra.org

#KYisComing #AStygianDawn #KY17 #Throwback

The nation is glistening with the sheen of diyas to blend with the Diwali festivities. Express and share the mirth of this festive season by capturing a picture of yourself enjoying these festive moments and sending us on our facebook page. Grab surprising gifts from KY upon getting maximum likes and shares for your post! 
Send your entries on www.fb.com/kashiyatra.iitbhu 
Rules:
1. Only those likes and shares would be considered who have liked the Kashiyatra Facebook page.
2. Message photo on the page with proper details including Name, Contact No and College Name.
3. Points system : 1 Like = 1 point; 1 Share = 3 point.
4. Entries would be taken till 23rd Oct, 2017 and the winner would be declared on 25th Oct, 2017.
5. Multiple shares by the same person at the same time and fake likes would lead to disqualification from the contest.

#Deepotsav #Diwali #Culture #Kashiyatra
#FestiveMoment #Celebration #Decoration #Preparation #Gifts
#KY18 #AStygianDawn‌

The wait has started. Just as the werewolf in the darkness longs for the full moon, so is the wait for KY'18, a Stygian dawn. The background is being setup for the three big nights like never before. Stay tuned!

#KY18  #AStygianDawn  #Cover
#WaitForWinter  #KYcomeswithwinter

KY'18 brings BLISS - The Inter-school Cultural Championship, presented by Toppr.com, co-sponsored by Ambition Gurukul and powered by Etoos India on 14th October, 2017. 
It is all about bringing the elements of our cultural heritage spanning over Dance, Music, Drama, Fine Arts ,Literature and Quiz under one banner. It creates a platform for the young students to showcase their talent, creativity and enthusiasm and uplift them to a competitive level. With the budding talents pitted against each other,  it truly caters to the idea of witnessing the rich culture we inherit through a young mind's view!

#Bliss #School #Cultural #Championship 
#Kashiyatra #KY18 #AStygianDawn
#WaitForWinter #KYcomeswithwinter
